Description: Sovereign athlete training log for deeper insights and smarter progress.
 MyTraL is a self-hosted Python/Flask web application for tracking athlete
 training data. Additional Python runtime dependencies not available as system
 packages (anthropic, bokeh, openai, polars, pydantic-ai-slim, structlog,
 fit-tool, rdp, polyline, flask-cors) must be installed via pip.
